{"tid":912881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"報喜！主播妻順產射手小帥哥 57歲哈林2子1女體力旺","createTime":"2018-11-23T04:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T00:23:02.000Z","uid":102732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6e45707692318bf1071b2301b9a1100a036e9d22","tid":912881,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%A6%BB%E9%A0%86%E7%94%A2%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%B8%A5%E5%93%A5-57%E6%AD%B2%E5%93%88%E6%9E%972%E5%AD%901%E5%A5%B3%E9%AB%94%E5%8A%9B%E6%97%BA-021029993.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2596%259C-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E9%25A0%2586%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B8%25A5%25E5%2593%25A5-57%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2593%2588%25E6%259E%25972%25E5%25AD%25901%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2597%25BA-021029993.html&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d563e099\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%A6%BB%E9%A0%86%E7%94%A2%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%B8%A5%E5%93%A5-57%E6%AD%B2%E5%93%88%E6%9E%972%E5%AD%901%E5%A5%B3%E9%AB%94%E5%8A%9B%E6%97%BA-021029993.html</a><br />\n<br />\n男星哈林 2016 年二婚小 14 歲主播張嘉欣，妻子隔年 6 月產下女兒「哈密瓜」，沒想到夫妻倆做人神速，愛女今（2018）年 7 月才滿周歲，就爆出 57 歲哈林又將再度當爸，他事後證實喜訊，透露老婆預產期在 11 月底，昨（ 22 ）日晚間傳出張嘉欣已順利產下一名男娃，母子均安。<br />\n<br />\n據《鏡週刊》報導，哈林妻子張嘉欣昨晚順利「卸貨」，寶寶是位射手座小帥哥，張嘉欣目前正於醫院靜養，哈林與妻子喜迎第二個小孩，加上與前妻伊能靜所生的兒子「小哈利」，哈林已是三度當爸，前陣子他受訪時感性地說：「我知道很多人沒有這麼容易、過程很辛苦，老天真的很照顧我，非常感恩」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，注重隱私的哈林鮮少談及家務事，但老當益壯的他，當年與美女主播張嘉欣低調完婚，妻子沒多久就傳出懷孕，老東家因此讓她留職停薪，誰知短時間內第二胎又來報到，讓張嘉欣重返主播台日子又往後延，而愛家的哈林也在結束大陸節目《中國好聲音》工作後，全心全意陪妻子待產，好爸爸、好老公形象受外界讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n個個男星都鍾意搵後生老婆生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw邊個叫哈林? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e0d35758e2d4ebcb902b4719b9c5da2e90f709","tid":912881,"uid":29080,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"哈林都唔識？個樣好似庾澄慶嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2196c7c7e8dc836bb9e2a428d18f1f82f5dc8380","tid":912881,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"男星哈林 2016 年二婚小 14 歲主播張嘉欣<br />\n<br />\n57-14 = 43<br />\n我睇錯定計錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e39247052058396a903e5019a58fcd8f8d8e537","tid":912881,"uid":68851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2196c7c7e8dc836bb9e2a428d18f1f82f5dc8380","tid":912881,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"男星哈林 2016 年二婚小 14 歲主播張嘉欣<br />\n<br />\n57-14 = 43<br />\n我睇錯定計錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"應該吹奏高齡產婦<br />\n而唔係吹奏辣殺哈林"},{"pid":"f75c4f756336cd24e2f14c6f42d645b6490ec9a5","tid":912881,"uid":74316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"佢個仔同庾澄慶 好似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603e170b32dc289aa9d3a50d9e7cf756deeb539c","tid":912881,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:42:57.000Z","msg":"恭喜佢<br />\n當年頂綠帽完美除下"},{"pid":"e7ddcad807681d792e9d9d836f02d8738b997e7b","tid":912881,"uid":102732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f75c4f756336cd24e2f14c6f42d645b6490ec9a5","tid":912881,"uid":74316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"佢個仔同庾澄慶 好似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as